-- PTT to Buy 2 Million Tons of LNG a Year From Qatar, IOD Says
-- B y   J a c o b   A d e l m a n
-- 2012-06-06T01:46:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-06/ptt-to-buy-2-million-tons-of-lng-a-year-from-qatar-iod-says.html
PTT Pcl (PTT)  plans to import 2 million
metric tons a year of liquefied natural gas from Qatar Liquefied
Gas Co., International Oil Daily reported, citing PTT President
Pailin Chuchottaworn.  PTT, Thailand’s largest energy company, will sign the
import contract with the company known as QatarGas “very
soon,” Chuchottaworn said in an interview yesterday during the
World Gas Conference in Kuala Lampur, according to IOD.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jacob Adelman in Tokyo at 
